  "intent_precise": "Sample Prep for ELISA Test: Using diluent_tubes (tuberack, slot 7), reagent (tuberack, slot 8), master_block (plate, slot 4). (1) Transfer 55\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (2) Mix mix_reps times at 20\u00b5L. (3) Transfer 40\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (4) Mix mix_reps times at 180\u00b5L. (5) Transfer 80\u00b5L from source (A1, A1) to destination (A1, A1). (6) Mix mix_reps times at 700\u00b5L. (7) Transfer from source A1 to destination A1. (8) Mix mix_reps times at 800\u00b5L. (9) Distribute from source A1 to destination wells A1. (10) Mix mix_reps times at 1.0mL.",
